üéµ AI-Based Music Recommendation System
Overview

This project implements a content-based music recommendation system using audio embeddings extracted by deep learning models.
Given a query music file, the system retrieves top-K similar tracks from a local music database.

Performance highlight

Recommendation precision: ~80% ‚ÄúGood‚Äù matches

Random baseline precision: ~20%

‚âà 4√ó improvement over random selection

System Architecture
Core Pipeline

Audio preprocessing

Extract audio features using librosa

Embedding extraction

Generate high-dimensional audio embeddings with torchopenl3

Similarity search

Index embeddings using FAISS

Perform nearest-neighbor search for recommendations

Inference

Given a query music file, return top-K most similar tracks

Tools & Technologies
Component	Tool
Audio processing	librosa
Audio embedding	torchopenl3
Vector indexing	faiss
ML framework	PyTorch
Containerization	Docker
Hardware	GPU (6 GB VRAM)
Resource & Performance Constraints

GPU memory: 6 GB

Embedding build time:

~5 minutes for 100 standard music files

Designed for local deployment with GPU acceleration

Engineering Considerations

Well-defined APIs for easy integration into full-stack applications

Docker-based environment isolation for reproducibility

Modular design for:

Data preprocessing

Embedding generation

Index building

Recommendation inference

Directory Structure
data/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ input/          # Query music files
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ movie_input/    # (Optional) Movie files for audio extraction
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ music_db/       # Music database for recommendation

Environment Setup
1. Build Docker Image

Build the Docker image using the provided Dockerfile.

2. Run Container
docker run --gpus all -it --rm \
  --mount type=bind,source="host_path",target=container_path \
  your_image_name bash

3. Install Project Dependencies

Inside the container:

cd <project_root>
pip install -e .


This ensures the project uses exact dependency versions.

Optional: Movie-to-Audio Conversion

Convert movie files into audio files for recommendation.

python app/converters/movie_convert.py \
  -i input_path \
  -o output_path

Supported Formats

.mp4

.mkv

.avi

.mov

.flv

Usage
1. Build Embeddings (One-time or after data update)
python app/recommend.py -b True


This:

Extracts embeddings from music_db

Builds the FAISS index

2. Run Recommendation
python app/recommend.py -r your_query_music_file


Returns Top-5 recommendations based on audio similarity.

